  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Water disaster Platform to enhance climate resilience in Africa</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project focuses on the development of flood early warning system and building capacity at local, national and regional levels on flood risk management. It will contribute to enhance the flood disaster resilience of the West Africa countries with a major focus on the countries belonging to the Niger basin Authority (NBA) and Volta Basin Authority (VBA). The project will set up a regional flood early warning system focusing on the Niger and Volta basins. The project will contribute to enhance the capacity of AGRHYMET, NBA, VBA and NBA and VBA countries on the management of flood disasters through integrated flood management approaches.</narrative>
  </description>
